Request for Loan 1. Quick Pay is a special feature provided by 3F Oil Palm so that Our farmers can get payment for their FFB supplied within 24 hrs. \n2. Complete calculation and value of payment will be mentioned in the receipt in the app. The receipt requires a digital signature of the farmer which signifies agreement to all terms and conditions. In case a 3FOP representative is raising a Quick Pay request on behalf of the farmer, then a 4 digit PIN number will be sent to the registered mobile number of the farmer. This will act as the confirmation to the agreement to all terms and conditions. \n3. To avail this offer, there is a flat transaction fee On actuals and per ton Quick Pay fee. \n4. Quick Pay will be paid based on the prevalent adhoc rate.In case adhoc rate is not yet known,Quick Pay will be based on an assumed adhoc rateBut it will be adjusted based on Government Order rate, As and when declared. When the Invoice Rate is declared,That adjustment will also take place, and will be paid Or deducted along with future payments (normal or Quick Pay). \n5. At least 1 unpaid collection is required in order to request for Quick Pay.In case of more than 1 unpaid collection,Quick Pay request will happen on all pending unpaid collections. \n6. All deductions from farmer or pending payments to farmer such as rate adjustments,Fertilizers, poles and labour requests that were done against FFB and are due by theFarmer to the company before the date of request of Quick Pay Will be reduced from the FFB payment while making Quick Pay payment. \n7. In order to be eligible for Quick Pay,FFB payment value should be greater than any against FFB deductions. \n8. If Quick Pay has already been requested,Another Quick Pay request cannot be requested until the 1st one is completed. \n9. Once Quick Pay has been requested, it cannot be cancelled. \n10. Quick Pay is not available on the date on which the company is processing regular farmer’s payment.Those dates will come twice a month according to regular pay cycle. \n11.In case labour service or product purchase done recently against FFB,it might not show in this payout statementbecause it is still under process. However,it will be deducted during Quick Pay payout.For details, pls see your farmer ledger.
